    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840683_5_8766-8794",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "8766-8794",
      "markText": "屠户见女婿衣裳后襟滚皱了许多，一路低着头替他扯了几十回。",
      "totalCount": 64,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840683&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=8766&rangeEnd=8794",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3e932df05cd3eb3e9b91c82?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=8766&rangeEnd=8794"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840683_24_7207-7233",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "7207-7233",
      "markText": "读书好，耕田好，学好便好；创业难，守成难，知难不难。",
      "totalCount": 60,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840683&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=7207&rangeEnd=7233",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3e932df05cd3eb3e9b91c82?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=7207&rangeEnd=7233"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840683_36_1926-1981",
      "chapterUid": 36,
      "range": "1926-1981",
      "markText": "大人已去，心里欢喜道：“好了！我做秀才，有了这一场结局。将来乡试也不应，科、岁也不考，逍遥自在，做些自己的事罢",
      "totalCount": 48,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840683&chapterUid=36&rangeStart=1926&rangeEnd=1981",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3e932df05cd3eb3e9b91c82?chapterUid=36&rangeStart=1926&rangeEnd=1981"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840683_5_2995-3032",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "2995-3032",
      "markText": "面吃苦久了，如今自己当权，须要把卷子都要细细看过，不可听着幕客，屈了真才。",
      "totalCount": 45,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840683&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2995&rangeEnd=3032",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3e932df05cd3eb3e9b91c82?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=2995&rangeEnd=3032"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840683_8_1302-1388",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "1302-1388",
      "markText": "“爷，只有我能知道你的心事。你是为那灯盏里点的是两茎灯草，不放心，恐费了油。我如今挑掉一茎就是了。”说罢，忙走去挑掉一茎。众人看严监生时，点一点头，把手垂下，登时就没了气。",
      "totalCount": 39,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840683&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1302&rangeEnd=1388",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3e932df05cd3eb3e9b91c82?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=1302&rangeEnd=1388"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840683_3_1411-1441",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "1411-1441",
      "markText": "但世人一见了功名，便舍着性命去求他，及至到手之后，味同嚼蜡。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840683&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1411&rangeEnd=1441",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3e932df05cd3eb3e9b91c82?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=1411&rangeEnd=1441"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840683_3_2463-2491",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "2463-2491",
      "markText": "又心里想道：“天下那有个学不会的事，我何不自画他几枝？”",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840683&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2463&rangeEnd=2491",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3e932df05cd3eb3e9b91c82?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=2463&rangeEnd=2491"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840683_3_3455-3475",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "3455-3475",
      "markText": "既不求官爵，又不交纳朋友，终日闭户读书。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840683&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3455&rangeEnd=3475",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3e932df05cd3eb3e9b91c82?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=3455&rangeEnd=3475"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840683_21_8024-8053",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "8024-8053",
      "markText": "匡超人不看便罢，看了这款单，不觉飕的一声，魂从顶门出去了。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840683&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=8024&rangeEnd=8053",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3e932df05cd3eb3e9b91c82?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=8024&rangeEnd=8053"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840683_3_4118-4193",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "4118-4193",
      "markText": "翟头役禀过了本官，那知县时仁，发出二十四两银子来。翟买办扣克了十二两，只拿十二两银子送与王冕，将册页取去。时知县又办了几样礼物，送与危素，作候问之礼。",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840683&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4118&rangeEnd=4193",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3e932df05cd3eb3e9b91c82?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=4118&rangeEnd=4193"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840683_3_9245-9268",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "9245-9268",
      "markText": "只见天上纷纷有百十个小星，都坠向东南角上去了。",
      "totalCount": 34,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840683&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=9245&rangeEnd=9268",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3e932df05cd3eb3e9b91c82?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=9245&rangeEnd=9268"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840683_4_1710-1795",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1710-1795",
      "markText": "正说着，外边走进一个人来，两只红眼边，一副锅铁脸，几根黄胡子，歪戴着瓦楞帽，身上青布衣服就如油篓一般；手里拿着一根赶驴的鞭子，走进门来，和众人拱一拱手，一屁股就坐在上席。",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840683&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1710&rangeEnd=1795",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3e932df05cd3eb3e9b91c82?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1710&rangeEnd=1795"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840683_8_2315-2367",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "2315-2367",
      "markText": "但自古道：‘公而忘私，国而忘家。’我们科场是朝廷大典，你我为朝廷办事，就是不顾私亲，也还觉得于心无愧。”",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840683&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2315&rangeEnd=2367",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3e932df05cd3eb3e9b91c82?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=2315&rangeEnd=2367"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840683_11_2606-2626",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "2606-2626",
      "markText": "而今人情薄了，这米做出来的酒汁都是薄的！",
      "totalCount": 32,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840683&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=2606&rangeEnd=2626",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3e932df05cd3eb3e9b91c82?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=2606&rangeEnd=2626"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840683_3_5604-5616",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "5604-5616",
      "markText": "将来志书上少不得称赞一篇",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840683&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5604&rangeEnd=5616",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3e932df05cd3eb3e9b91c82?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=5604&rangeEnd=5616"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840683_8_5897-5965",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "5897-5965",
      "markText": "放你的狗屁！我因素日有个晕病，费了几百两银子合了这一料药，是省里张老爷在上党做官带了来的人参，周老爷在四川做官带了来的黄连！你这奴才！‘",
      "totalCount": 30,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=840683&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=5897&rangeEnd=5965",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/3e932df05cd3eb3e9b91c82?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=5897&rangeEnd=5965"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "840683_22_5265-5337",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "5265-5337",
